  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Moon White is a short and easy action game featuring Chinese Kungfu. It tells about a journey how two elves compete with each other, looking for the harmony of traditional dance in each movement and posture.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812480/extras/92b13c7b5eda212afced42f48396bfe5.apng?t=1737084845\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812480/extras/92b13c7b5eda212afced42f48396bfe5.poster.avif?t=1737084845\" class=\"bb_img\" width=240 height=240 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Up to 48 postures with different pace and speed to explore. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Low difficulty and no health point. Try any times if you want. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Feel different seasons in the three different levels. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812480/extras/526646d096724125dfacb3dffda46928.apng?t=1737084845\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812480/extras/526646d096724125dfacb3dffda46928.poster.avif?t=1737084845\" class=\"bb_img\" width=216 height=180 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rules</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Play the role of Luna to respond Blanc's continual movement and action.<br>* Press the guard key at the perfect time to resolve the difficulty. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* The more combo you get, the higher stage you will reach.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Moon White is a short and easy action game featuring Chinese Kungfu. It tells about a journey how two elves compete with each other, looking for the harmony of traditional dance in each movement and posture.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812480/extras/92b13c7b5eda212afced42f48396bfe5.apng?t=1737084845\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812480/extras/92b13c7b5eda212afced42f48396bfe5.poster.avif?t=1737084845\" class=\"bb_img\" width=240 height=240 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Up to 48 postures with different pace and speed to explore. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Low difficulty and no health point. Try any times if you want. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Feel different seasons in the three different levels. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812480/extras/526646d096724125dfacb3dffda46928.apng?t=1737084845\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812480/extras/526646d096724125dfacb3dffda46928.poster.avif?t=1737084845\" class=\"bb_img\" width=216 height=180 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rules</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Play the role of Luna to respond Blanc's continual movement and action.<br>* Press the guard key at the perfect time to resolve the difficulty. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* The more combo you get, the higher stage you will reach.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
